Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.92,0:00:14.93,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.20,0:00:15.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.83,0:00:18.91,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:23.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:26.79,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:30.45,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.45,0:00:34.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.10,0:00:36.84,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.77,0:00:40.30,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:45.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.06,0:00:48.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:51.20,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.31,0:00:54.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.90,0:00:59.54,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:03.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:11.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:13.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:15.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.38,0:01:18.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Lightning won't strike a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.47,0:01:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But lightning\Nreally scares me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.97,0:01:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Rain, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.21,0:01:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.10,0:01:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Toshiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.52,0:01:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't rain... it's sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.07,0:01:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sand, falling from the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.08,0:01:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.52,0:02:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use.\NYukiko, take the wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll push.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so much sand...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.27,0:02:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is awful...\NWhat's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.56,0:02:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.21,0:02:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to get out of\Nhere as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We will.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.22,0:02:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When I give the\Nsignal, slam the gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.30,0:02:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Toshiki, the car!\NThe car is sinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.46,0:02:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Toshiki, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.35,0:02:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker's artificial\Nantlion pit is a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The antlion pits that\NI, Jigoku Thunder, create
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.80,0:03:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,will tear apart\NJapanese roadways.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.28,0:03:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker will take advantage of the\Nchaos to begin its main offensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:19.28,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs143\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(477.167,230.389)}The Terrifying Antlion Pit
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why so timid, fools?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as the great Jigoku Thunder stands\Namong you, Shocker's Japan Branch will...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We have orders from our leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.09,0:03:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Zol has been dispatched to become\Ncommander-in-chief of the Japan Branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Zol?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.55,0:03:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The most powerful\Nman in all Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Your uniform is sloppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sloppy uniforms mean\Nsloppy soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I'm here,\Nwe'll be running a tight ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Colonel Zol.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency orders from\NFBI central headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.39,0:04:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,"Colonel Zol, a high commander with Shocker\Nwho we've been tracking for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.69,0:04:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,has transferred from Shocker's Near and\NMiddle East Branch to its Japan Branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be on high alert."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Zol...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He's killed countless skilled FBI agents\Nwho've pursued Shocker in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to avenge\Nmy colleagues!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:48.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Unexplained cave-ins have been\Noccurring across major roadways
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:53.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,all over the Japanese mainland,\Ncausing major traffic snarls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:56.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The government has\Nlaunched an inquiry, but so
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:04:59.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,far, they're no closer\Nto finding a solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.09,0:05:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems fishy to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.71,0:05:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's no way those amateurs\Nwill be able to find Shocker's trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.67,0:05:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! It's time for you two\Nto take action, then, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's going to happen\Nin an area like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd better take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, find anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, want to hit a rest stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.81,0:06:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a thrill-seeker, you know.\NI came hoping for some excitement...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough of that, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.56,0:06:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace and quiet is always best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.07,0:06:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Money's on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Zol,\NI have Taki Kazuya's voice on tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A picture of Taki and a\Nrecording of his voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.15,0:07:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I have all I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sending agents into\Nthe enemy ranks...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's how I crushed all resistance to\NShocker in the Near and Middle East.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.43,0:07:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I'm here in Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I will put an end to Shocker's hated\Nenemy, the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Money's on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:23.62,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\c&H170480&\3c&HFFFFFF&}No Entry
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.63,0:08:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Reporting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.57,0:08:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- Get him! \N- Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.37,0:09:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- Go that way! \N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.68,0:09:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.76,0:09:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now,\Nhave a good look at my face...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like the\Nlook of those clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's more than\Njust the clouds...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.91,0:10:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was\Nraining, but it's sand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, head back and stop any\Nother cars coming this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.74,0:10:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Traffic duty, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I always wanted to try that once.\N It's pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this irresponsible\Ngirl and head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do, Hayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see for myself\Nwhat happens next.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...\NI knew Shocker was behind this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.53,0:10:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can stand against Shocker?\NYou fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:10:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider... plunge into the\Nantlion pit of Jigoku Thunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.29,0:11:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.72,0:12:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Great though your powers may be,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,they are worthless\Nin my antlion pit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope Taki and Yuri\Nare doing all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:44.94,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(331,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.53,0:12:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:12:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing,\Ndirecting traffic?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:12:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous up ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even police\Nshould go through.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Mr. Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There's been a cave-in down the\Nroad two kilometers from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.44,0:13:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're under arrest for murder\Nand interfering with an officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.74,0:13:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.65,0:13:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.83,0:13:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb!\NWe know everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the one who\Nattacked us earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.48,0:13:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.31,0:13:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get to the bottom of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're taking you to the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really\Ngoing to arrest me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.26,0:13:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you resisting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There's been some\Nkind of mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.39,0:13:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But an investigation will\Nclear my name easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.64,0:13:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go along with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.76,0:13:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell Hayato what happened here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.72,0:13:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Come along!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.11,0:13:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki Kazuya...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You can sate yourself on\Nprison meals for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:14:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.75,0:14:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Five, six, seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No visitors until the\Ninvestigation is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.71,0:14:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's ridiculous.\NMr. Taki can't be a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I was with him all day!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I was there on the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I know he's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you at the scene as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.64,0:14:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I was one of the men injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.23,0:14:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never forget the face\Nof the man who did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.69,0:14:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now get lost, before we charge\Nyou as accessories to murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.65,0:14:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.06,0:14:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a lady.\NI wouldn't hurt a fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's head back to\Nthe club for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't sulk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But can't a murder conviction\Nlead to the death penalty?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.68,0:14:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki hasn't done anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't put\Ninnocent men to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.97,0:14:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But the witnesses...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go see Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you going to see\Nhim, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use a few drastic measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.82,0:15:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Five, six, seven, eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.06,0:15:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.63,0:15:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.94,0:15:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you come here\Nto vouch for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes,\Nbut they wouldn't accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They claim they saw your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.67,0:15:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This could be a Shocker trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But why only set\Nthe trap for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They must have a cyborg\Nthat's copied your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.38,0:15:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.19,0:16:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.54,0:16:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but they may not believe that\Nthere's another man out there
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,who looks exactly like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato, get me out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to catch the impostor\Nand prove my innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you escape now,\Nyou'll look more guilty than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.34,0:16:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What if that Shocker cyborg\Nno longer looks like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.61,0:16:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How would we prove your\Ninnocence, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.39,0:16:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Just sit tight for a\Nwhile, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.15,0:16:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You insensitive fool, Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Are you trying to\Nbreak into the station?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Help!\N- Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.44,0:16:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri and Goro are\Ncausing trouble again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang tight, Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hay...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.91,0:16:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad! You made it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to worry\Nyou, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,See...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.99,0:17:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,After you left,\NI was attacked by Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.94,0:17:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They arrested him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked exactly like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, they let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They thought they could\Ndivide and conquer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.33,0:17:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm glad you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.37,0:17:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll resume our highway\Ninvestigations tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.85,0:17:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna come tomorrow, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for women and\Nchildren to head home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be like that!\NPlease, Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.74,0:17:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.67,0:18:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's do some\Nprep work for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll destroy Ichimonji Hayato\Nwith this time bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, victory will be ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.78,0:18:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you so sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.39,0:18:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.51,0:18:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Only my friends call me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:18:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker cyborg!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.69,0:19:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen through your trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.53,0:19:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.75,0:19:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.\NThe resemblance is uncanny...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.61,0:19:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.02,0:19:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki Kazuya is part of the FBI's\NShocker investigation team.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They used their influence\Nto get him released.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If the jig is up,\NI can abandon this face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.41,0:19:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to introduce myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Formerly head of Shocker's\NNear and Middle East Branch,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.99,0:19:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,now deployed to their Japan Branch...\NColonel Zol.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A senior Shocker commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.38,0:19:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All who hear my name
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.67,0:19:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and see my face must die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.94,0:19:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.18,0:20:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll handle the small fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.56,0:20:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.41,0:20:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This time,\NI'll finish your bike with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.19,0:20:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one\Nway to escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.63,0:22:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.53,0:23:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.46,0:23:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Our highways are safe again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.35,0:23:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.27,0:23:13.23,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Jigoku Thunder will be avenged.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.80,0:23:15.74,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,As long as I,\NColonel Zol, am here,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.74,0:23:19.74,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Shocker's conquest of\NJapan is inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.80,0:23:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mukadelas!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.47,0:23:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin preparations for\Nyour operation at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.03,0:23:35.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What is the nature of this new\NShocker cyborg, Mukadelas?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.00,0:23:37.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And what is Shocker plotting?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.02,0:23:40.55,Cont,,0,0,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,470)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.98,0:23:43.46,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.98,0:23:44.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.97,0:23:46.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the monstrous Mukadelas!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.45,0:23:50.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The monstrous Mukadelas uses hypnotic\Nwaves to kidnap intelligent children.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.42,0:23:52.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Goro is made to\Njoin Junior Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.52,0:23:55.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mukadelas attacks Ichimonji\NHayato and Taki Kazuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.60,0:24:00.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for more Kamen Rider\Nin "Mukadelas' Monster School!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.35,0:24:00.93,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,650.389)}Mukadelas' Monster School!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.13,0:24:10.97,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.55,0:24:13.55,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.55,0:24:15.51,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.51,0:24:18.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.06,0:24:20.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.94,0:24:22.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.81,0:24:24.61,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.61,0:24:26.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.40,0:24:28.44,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.49,0:24:34.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.16,0:24:37.74,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.74,0:24:41.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.83,0:24:45.59,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!